room_title: Escape room "Inheritance" by Sixth Sense Escape Games in Oklahoma City
room_address: 3705 W Memorial Rd #309 Oklahoma City, OK 73134
room_description: Your great uncle has sadly passed away. You learn that your real inheritance was hidden in the attic of his old house. You have one hour to get in and claim it before the demolition takes place. Claiming your fortune and getting out in time will be harder than you think!
